<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/destyle.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/confirm.css"/>
<title><%= title %></title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <p>登録内容に間違いはありませんか？</p>
            <table>
                <% for(let i in formVal){ %>
                    <tr>
                        <th><%= formName[i] %></th>
                        <td><%= formVal[i] %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% } %>
            </table>

            <form action="/users/confirm" method="post">
                <button name="btn" value="back">戻る</button>
                <button name="btn" value="insert">登録</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>